"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here with Scotty's Fermented Foods. When you eat fermented foods, you get way more nutritional value and they're way more digestible than raw foods. And that's a hell of a thing to say because anytime you process foods, you generally make them less nutritious. But in the case of fermented foods, you're recruiting bacteria to process the vegetables. Anauric bacteria eat the sugars out of the vegetable, and in doing so, they break down the cellular wall to get to those sugars. It's the same way you digest. You have anaerobic bacteria in your gut that break down the cell wall to get to the calories and to get to the nutrients that are in the vegetable. So when you're eating fermented foods, it's like they're almost pre-digested for you. Much more digestible, much more nutritionally available, up to ten times more. And that's an incredible thing to say. You should eat lots of them and you can get them at Scotty'sFoods.com. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here with Scotty's Fermented Foods.\",\n      \"start\": 0.48,\n      \"end\": 3.44,\n      \"duration\": 2.96,\n      \"confidence\": 0.989,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.72,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n   